sources.title: 1933 Der Tunnel ( Paul Hartmann, Attila Hörbiger, Gustaf Gründgens, Otto Wernicke, Josef Eichheim)
sources.description: Film aus dem deutschen dritten Reich von 1933. Der Tunnel.  U.a mit Attila Hörbiger und Gustaf Gründgens

metadata.Plot: An engineer is hired to plan and oversee the construction of a undersea tunnel between Europe and the US. However, certain interests don't want to see the tunnel built and use every means at their disposal, including sabotage and murder, to stop its construction.
metadata.Writer: Curtis Bernhardt, Bernhard Kellermann, Henry Koster
metadata.Actors: Paul Hartmann, Attila Hörbiger, Olly von Flint
